T1  - Sensitivity Analysis of Cost Coefficient Estimates: The Case of Linear Decision Rules for Employment and Production
AU  - Van De Panne, C.
AU  - Bosje, P.
Y1  - 1962/10/01
PY  - 1962
DA  - 1962/10/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.9.1.82
